## How Concierge AI Takes Actions Instead Of Just Answering Questions

**What it does:**
- Creates expenses (receipt, cash, distance)
- Extracts receipt data automatically
- Deletes expenses when requested

**Customer value:**
- Reduces manual data entry
- Saves time for employees
- Turns chat into action

**Talk track:**
- “It doesn’t just tell you what to do—it actually does the work for you.”

